item.title: CVE-2019-5089|2024-08-04T19:47:56.083Z -- investintech%20inc. -- able2extract%20professional
item.description: An exploitable memory corruption vulnerability exists in Investintech Able2Extract Professional 4.0.7 x64. A specially crafted JPEG file can cause an out-of-bounds memory write, allowing an attacker to execute arbitrary code on the victim machine. An attacker could exploit a vulnerability by providing the user with a specially crafted JPEG file.
